The Queen actress Jessica Nkosi’s management has raised the alarm about scammers who pose as Nkosi on social media. “Miss Nkosi is neither involved in nor advertising Bitcoin or any form of cryptocurrency,” reads the statement from her management, advising all the people who have fallen prey to the scam to report to cyber-crime authorities. See statement below:  For the latest entertainment news from Sunday World, click here. Or read the latest from Shwashwi here. Follow @SundayWorldZA on Twitter and @sundayworldza on Instagram, or like our Facebook Page, Sunday World, by clicking here for the latest breaking news in South Africa. To Subscribe to Sunday World, click here.